<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>

<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> shaft with well cut moulded panels on three sides (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.42</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">1.13</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.40</measure>); inscribed on the face (panel <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.26</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.97</measure>). </p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face. Top has square cutting in centre; the text must have begun on an upper feature.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>standard forms; ave <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025</measure>, Φ <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03</measure>; ligatured ΤΗ in ll. 6, 7, ΜΝ and ΜΗ in l.12; apices slanting down from left to right over initial Ι in l. 5, Υ and Ι in l. 6, and from right to left above Ρ in l.5.</p>
</div>
