<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>The Chrysophoroi are the neopoioi; see word index</p>
<p>Julius Aurelius Ktesias might be the envoy to Gordian (A &amp; R 21.8); but another candidate is T.Claudius Aurelius Ktesias, rhetor, see <xref type="iAph">1794</xref>, (CIG 2797 = LBW 1598) ? also in <xref type="iAph">1723</xref> and <xref type="iAph">1027</xref> (= 64.427 and MAMA 497)</p>
</div>
